        <http://example.org/recipes/plato-principal/2/step/bb0229e4ce7c47c3a43f14b6b7af55ec>,
        <http://example.org/recipes/plato-principal/2/step/c147d52938e644b7b55fc5651f1bbe4d>,
        <http://example.org/recipes/plato-principal/2/step/c41094d2f1d4411697e743ac690665a3>,
